        "action": "Establish instant lockdown alert system for schools, nurseries & parents",
        "additional_details": "We believe that we need a national instant alert system so schools, nurseries and even parents are notified immediately, given clear information, and told when lockdowns have ended.",
        "background": "The Government should introduce a national instant alert system so schools, nurseries, and parents are directly notified by authorities when a lockdown is required and when it has ended.",
